'''IDF:''' at least 250 militants<ref>Carmela Menashe, [http://www.iba.org.il/bet/?type=1&entity=1025694 <U+05E9><U+05D9><U+05D9><U+05D8><U+05EA> 13 <U+05E4><U+05D2><U+05E2><U+05D4> <U+05D1><U+05DE><U+05E9><U+05D2><U+05E8><U+05D9><U+05DD> <U+05D1><U+05E8><U+05E6><U+05D5><U+05E2><U+05D4>; 4 <U+05D7><U+05D9><U+05D9><U+05DC><U+05D9><U+05DD> <U+05E0><U+05E4><U+05E6><U+05E2><U+05D5> <U+05E7><U+05DC>], [[Kol Yisrael|Kol Yisrael - Reshet Beth]], 13 July 2014</ref><ref>[http://www.mako.co.il/news-military/security/Article-2d9003dceb85741004.htm <U+05DE><U+05D0><U+05D6> <U+05D4><U+05DB><U+05E0><U+05D9><U+05E1><U+05D4> <U+05DC><U+05E2><U+05D6><U+05D4>: 150 <U+05DE><U+05D7><U+05D1><U+05DC><U+05D9><U+05DD> <U+05D7><U+05D5><U+05E1><U+05DC><U+05D5>, 16 <U+05DE><U+05E0><U+05D4><U+05E8><U+05D5><U+05EA> <U+05E0><U+05D7><U+05E9><U+05E4><U+05D5>], [[Mako (website)|mako]]-[[Channel 2 (Israel)|Channel 2]] News, 21 July 2014</ref>

